genresAdvancedInfo.name: rock dominicano
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Rock Dominicano is a genre of rock music that originated in the Dominican Republic. It is heavily influenced by traditional Dominican music, such as merengue and bachata, and combines these elements with rock instrumentation. The lyrics often touch on themes of love, social issues, and personal struggles. Bands such as Toque Profundo and Rita Indiana y Los Misterios have helped popularize Rock Dominicano.
